item.title: ZW32-12G-outdoor-high-voltage-vacuum-circuit-breaker
item.description: ZW32-12(G)/T series outdoor high-voltage AC intelligent vacuum circuit breaker is an outdoor high-voltage power distribution switchgear with a rated voltage of 12kV and three-phase AC 50Hz, mainly used for breaking, It can close the load current, overload current and short-circuit current in the power system. It is suitable for protection and control in the power distribution system of substations and industrial and mining enterprises, and can also be used in places that require frequent operations such as rural power grids.
